pullRequest.body:
Add a CI step to make sure that if `assert_not_exists X` appears in a file, then `X` is actually defined somewhere in `Mathlib`.

Until #15732 is merged, the test should fail, since there are currently declarations in `assert_not_exists` that not only do not exist in the file, but do not exist at all.
